Interface TagStack

All Known Implementing Classes:
BaseTagStack, HtmlTagStack, ImmutableTagStack, MutableTagStack, XmlTagStack
public interface TagStack

Interface for representing and accessing a stack of xml tags.

Author:

getTags

java.util.List<XmlLite.Tag> getTags()
Get a copy of the current stack from the top (root) to the bottom (farthest from root).

NOTE: The result is a copy of the current stack and will not be effected by subsequent stack operations.
